| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2538 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f7cd6bb0-38fa-590c-8853-c8bddbfe1ae6"
